- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

10:36.460 --> 10:38.178
- I JUST--MAYBE I
SHOULD WALK OVER THERE.

10:38.220 --> 10:39.494
- I DON'T WANT TO DO THAT.
- JUST--WHAT?

10:39.530 --> 10:40.906
- KRISTINA, YOU CAN'T DO THAT.
- TELL US WHAT THEY'RE SAYING.

10:40.950 --> 10:42.110
- I CAN'T DO THAT.
- WHY?

10:42.150 --> 10:43.253
- BECAUSE YOU'RE HEADMASTER
BRAVERMAN RIGHT NOW, OKAY?

10:43.290 --> 10:44.279
- YEAH.
- YOU'VE GOT SWITCH OFF

10:44.330 --> 10:45.911
MOM E40DE.

10:45.950 --> 10:47.326
- YOU'VE GOT TO TREAT MAX
LIKE ANY OTHER KID HERE.

10:47.370 --> 10:48.189
OKAY?
- OKAY.

10:48.230 --> 10:49.390
- HE'S FINE.
- OKAY.

10:49.440 --> 10:50.953
- HE'S OKAY.
- I'M NOT GONNA DO IT.

10:50.990 --> 10:52.810
- ALL RIGHT. YEAH.

10:52.850 --> 10:54.192
WHY DON'T YOU GO BACK
TO YOUR KITCHEN?

10:54.230 --> 10:55.436
- OH, SO YOU CAN WALK OVER THERE
AND CHECK UP ON THEM?

10:55.480 --> 10:56.788
- I WASN'T GONNA DO THAT.
- YOU WEREN'T?

10:56.820 --> 10:57.787
- I WASN'T.
- YOU SURE?

10:57.820 --> 10:59.060
- YOU HAVE TRUST ISSUES.
- DO I?

10:59.100 --> 11:00.306
- YOU DO.
- OKAY, LOOK ME IN THE EYE.

11:00.340 --> 11:02.137
ARE YOU GONNA WALK OVER THERE?

