ARE YOU?

11:03.240 --> 11:04.446
- NO.

11:04.490 --> 11:05.752
- NO?

11:07.390 --> 11:08.721
- THAT DOESN'T MAKE
ANY SENSE.

11:08.770 --> 11:10.658
- YES, IT DOES.

11:16.220 --> 11:18.780
- HI, SARAH.
- HI.

11:18.810 --> 11:20.493
- UH, IS HANK HERE?

11:20.540 --> 11:23.293
- OH, HI SANDY.
UM, HANK IS NOT.

11:23.330 --> 11:27.334
HE'S AT A JOB.

11:27.370 --> 11:30.191
HE SHOULD BE HERE PRETI'Y SOON
IF YOU WANT TO WAIT, OR--

11:30.240 --> 11:32.094
- THANKS, THAT'S OKAY.

11:32.130 --> 11:35.167
COULD YOU PLEASE JUST TELL HIM
THAT I STOPPED BY?

11:35.210 --> 11:36.234
- OF COURSE.
- THANK YOU.

11:36.280 --> 11:38.100
- SURE.

11:38.140 --> 11:40.199
HEY, SAN DY.

11:40.250 --> 11:43.378
YOU KNOW, IF YOU GUYS COULD USE
ANY HELP, YOU AND RUBY,

11:43.420 --> 11:45.832
I KNOW THE AREA REALLY WELL

11:45.870 --> 11:48.839
AND I MOVED HERE MYSELF
WITH TWO TEENAGERS,

11:48.880 --> 11:52.464
AND IT'S A BIG TRANSITION,
AND SO--

11:52.500 --> 11:55.799
- LISTEN, I KNOW
THAT YOU WORK FOR HANK AND YOU--

11:55.850 --> 11:57.294
- WE WORK TOGETHER,
BUT I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

11:57.330 --> 12:00.015
- OKAY, I THINK YOU TWO
ARE APPARENTLY DATING.

12:00.060 --> 12:01.368
WHAT GOES ON BETWEEN YOU GUYS--

12:01.410 --> 12:03.059
IT'S NOT MY BUSINESS,

12:03.100 --> 12:07.309
AND THIS IS NOTHING PERSONAL
AGAINST YOU,

12:07.340 --> 12:09.092
BUT I MOVED BACK HERE

12:09.140 --> 12:11.233
SO THAT RUBY COULD SPEND
MORE TIME WITH HER DAD.

12:11.280 --> 12:14.169
AND I--I JUST DON'T FEEL
THAT THAT TIME

12:14.210 --> 12:17.384
NEEDS TO INCLUDE YOU.

12:17.420 --> 12:19.832
AND I FEEL LIKE I WAS

12:19.870 --> 12:23.567
PRETI'Y CLEAR ABOUT THAT
WITH HANK.

12:23.600 --> 12:26.182
- OH, YOU'VE ALREADY HAD
THAT DISCUSSION WITH HIM?

12:26.220 --> 12:27.972
- YEAH.
- RIGHT. OKAY.

12:28.020 --> 12:30.329
UM, OKAY, WELL--

12:30.370 --> 12:32.395
- UM, COULD YOU PLEASE
JUST BE SURE

12:32.440 --> 12:34.840
THAT YOU TELL HIM
THAT I STOPPED BY?

12:34.890 --> 12:36.266
- MM-HMM.

12:36.300 --> 12:38.882
- ALL RIGHT. THANK YOU.

12:38.930 --> 12:40.329
- BYE.

12:48.280 --> 12:50.032
- OUR JOURNEY
OF SELF-DISCOVERY--

12:50.070 --> 12:52.140
NAMASTE.
- OH MY GOD.

12:52.180 --> 12:55.240
I CANNOT BEGIN TO TELL YOU
WHAT AN IDIOT OLIVER ROME IS.

12:55.290 --> 12:57.975
HE'S ON TOUR MAKING A TON
OF MONEY, HAVING A BLAST--

12:58.010 --> 12:59.284
