THE KIDS REALLY RESPONDED.

19:54.600 --> 19:55.771
- THAT'S NOT WHAT WE DO HERE.

19:55.810 --> 19:57.220
THAT IS NOT WHAT WE DO HERE.
- OKAY.

19:57.260 --> 19:58.568
- OKAY?
- SORRY.

19:58.610 --> 20:00.009
- OKAY.
- OKAY.

20:00.060 --> 20:02.631
- YOU'RE DISMISSED.

20:02.680 --> 20:04.329
- OH, SO I CAN GO?

20:04.370 --> 20:05.712
- GO TO CLASS.
- OKAY.

20:05.750 --> 20:06.956
THANK YOU, MRS. BRAVERMAN.
- THANK YOU.

20:10.830 --> 20:15.722
- OH.
GOSH, SHE'S BEAUTIFUL.

20:15.760 --> 20:18.888
IT'S SO GOOD SHE DOESN'T HAVE
HER FATHER'S NOSE.

20:18.940 --> 20:21.579
- [laughs]
THANK GOD FOR THAT.

20:23.800 --> 20:25.688
HOW'S HE DOING?

20:25.740 --> 20:26.695
- HE'S OKAY.

20:26.740 --> 20:29.561
