PUTTING OUT A FIRE FOR WORK.

20:29.600 --> 20:31.352
- IT'S SO COOL
THAT YOU HAVE YOUR BED

20:31.400 --> 20:33.630
IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE LIVING ROOM, GRANDPA.

20:33.680 --> 20:36.808
- YEAH, IT IS COOL,
ISN'T IT?

20:36.850 --> 20:38.989
HEY, JABBAR,
COME HERE A MINUTE.

20:39.030 --> 20:41.749
HOP DOWN THERE.

20:41.790 --> 20:44.998
NOW, HAVE YOU HEARD
ABOUT THE ICE TEA RELAY THING?

20:45.030 --> 20:46.713
- NO.

20:46.760 --> 20:48.614
- OH. SURPRISED--
IT'S BEEN GOING AROUND.

